The only one
I can be with forever is Ming'an.

34
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:46,540
Collector's edition.

35
00:01:53,060 --> 00:01:53,900
You...

36
00:01:55,660 --> 00:01:56,500
He Anran,

37
00:01:57,260 --> 00:01:58,620
you are my wife.

38
00:01:59,140 --> 00:02:01,620
You are destined
to stay with me forever.

39
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:08,620
Helian Zheng.

40
00:02:20,820 --> 00:02:21,660
Mr. Chu.

41
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:23,020
Do you still want to watch?

42
00:02:23,940 --> 00:02:25,260
This is a daily amusement

43
00:02:25,420 --> 00:02:26,980
between Anran and me.

44
00:02:27,210 --> 00:02:28,050
Helian Zheng.

45
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:28,900
And you,

46
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:31,020
you'll never have such a chance.

47
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:31,880
Helian Zheng.

48
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:34,260
You can't even think about it.

49
00:02:35,380 --> 00:02:36,420
Shameless!

50
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,340
She is your sister.

51
00:02:38,740 --> 00:02:39,620
So what?

52
00:02:39,820 --> 00:02:40,660
Anran!

53
00:02:41,140 --> 00:02:42,260
- Let go.
- We're married.

54
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:44,520
We're destined
to be together forever.

55
00:02:45,020 --> 00:02:45,860
Let go of me.

56
00:02:45,980 --> 00:02:46,820
Lieutenant Li,

57
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:48,140
see him out.

58
00:02:50,060 --> 00:02:51,780
Mr. Chu, this way.

59
00:02:52,380 --> 00:02:53,220
No need.

60
00:02:54,820 --> 00:02:55,660
I'll leave by myself.

61
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:58,740
Ming'an, I...

62
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:03,020
Helian Zheng.

63
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:05,540
Helian Zheng,

64
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,860
must you humiliate me
in front of others?

65
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:10,780
Humiliate?

66
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:13,940
He Anran.

67
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:15,820
If you think this is humiliation,

68
00:03:18,180 --> 00:03:19,900
it's far too lenient.

69
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:22,540
Let go of me.

70
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:23,820
Listen,

71
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:26,540
it doesn't have to be you.

72
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:30,820
Lieutenant Li, invite Miss Wen over.

73
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:32,520
The servants have the day off.

74
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:35,020
Anran will personally entertain.

75
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:38,820
Didn't you say no more matchmaking?

76
00:03:40,380 --> 00:03:41,660
Why should I listen to you?

77
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:44,820
If you want your father
to be comfortable in jail,

78
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:48,860
you'd better behave.

79
00:04:05,300 --> 00:04:06,400
Sorry to keep you waiting.

80
00:04:07,540 --> 00:04:08,380
Have a seat.

81
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:23,940
Your presence is an honor.

82
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,180
It's worth waiting.

83
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:27,300
We just received some new tea.

84
00:04:27,780 --> 00:04:29,300
Would you like to try some?

85
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:32,100
Serve the tea.

86
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,460
If it's your command,

87
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:40,700
and it pleases you,

88
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:43,780
then I shall comply.

89
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:50,820
Governor, who is this lady?

90
00:04:52,940 --> 00:04:54,020
She's insignificant.

91
