117
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:42,420
I'll ask Lieutenant Li to come over.

118
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:46,500
What?

119
00:06:47,220 --> 00:06:48,460
Are you not satisfied yet?

120
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:50,940
Or have you thought of

121
00:06:50,940 --> 00:06:52,220
new ways to insult me?

122
00:07:03,620 --> 00:07:06,060
Today's meeting with you was quite sudden.

123
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:08,140
Recently,

124
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:10,860
