has made city news.

125
00:07:11,540 --> 00:07:12,780
I don't know

126
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:15,140
why Mr. Zhao arranged this meeting.

127
00:07:15,900 --> 00:07:18,420
But seeing your wife today

128
00:07:18,940 --> 00:07:20,660
makes me realize that she's unique.

129
00:07:22,100 --> 00:07:23,420
It satisfies my curiosity.

130
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:26,500
